<!-- HEADER -->
<h1>Ozempic for Weight Loss: A Doctor's Complete Guide (2025)</h1>

<!-- AUTHOR BOX - Replace with your info -->
<div class="author-box">
    <div class="author-image">üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è</div>
    <div>
        <strong>Written by Dr. [Your Name], MD</strong><br>
        Internal Medicine Physician ‚Ä¢ [Your Hospital/Clinic]<br>
        <em>Medical review completed: February 2025</em>
    </div>
